11#ifndef MODULES_REMOTE_BITRATE_ESTIMATOR_REMOTE_BITRATE_ESTIMATOR_SINGLE_STREAM_H_
12#define MODULES_REMOTE_BITRATE_ESTIMATOR_REMOTE_BITRATE_ESTIMATOR_SINGLE_STREAM_H_
13
14#include <stddef.h>
15#include <stdint.h>
16
17#include <map>
18#include <memory>
19#include <vector>
20
21#include "api/transport/field_trial_based_config.h"
22#include "modules/remote_bitrate_estimator/aimd_rate_control.h"
23#include "modules/remote_bitrate_estimator/include/remote_bitrate_estimator.h"
24#include "rtc_base/rate_statistics.h"
25#include "rtc_base/synchronization/mutex.h"
26#include "rtc_base/thread_annotations.h"
27
28namespace webrtc {
29
30class Clock;
31struct RTPHeader;
32
33class RemoteBitrateEstimatorSingleStream : public RemoteBitrateEstimator {
34 public:
35 RemoteBitrateEstimatorSingleStream(RemoteBitrateObserver* observer,
36 Clock* clock);
37
38 RemoteBitrateEstimatorSingleStream() = delete;
39 RemoteBitrateEstimatorSingleStream(
40 const RemoteBitrateEstimatorSingleStream&) = delete;
41 RemoteBitrateEstimatorSingleStream& operator=(
42 const RemoteBitrateEstimatorSingleStream&) = delete;
43
44 ~RemoteBitrateEstimatorSingleStream() override;
45
46 void IncomingPacket(int64_t arrival_time_ms,
47 size_t payload_size,
48 const RTPHeader& header) override;
49 void Process() override;
50 int64_t TimeUntilNextProcess() override;
51 void OnRttUpdate(int64_t avg_rtt_ms, int64_t max_rtt_ms) override;
52 void RemoveStream(uint32_t ssrc) override;
53 bool LatestEstimate(std::vector<uint32_t>* ssrcs,
54 uint32_t* bitrate_bps) const override;
55 void SetMinBitrate(int min_bitrate_bps) override;
56
57 private:
58 struct Detector;
59
60 typedef std::map<uint32_t, Detector*> SsrcOveruseEstimatorMap;
61
62 // Triggers a new estimate calculation.
63 void UpdateEstimate(int64_t time_now) RTC_EXCLUSIVE_LOCKS_REQUIRED(mutex_);
64
65 void GetSsrcs(std::vector<uint32_t>* ssrcs) const
66 RTC_SHARED_LOCKS_REQUIRED(mutex_);
67
68 // Returns |remote_rate_| if the pointed to object exists,
69 // otherwise creates it.
70 AimdRateControl* GetRemoteRate() RTC_EXCLUSIVE_LOCKS_REQUIRED(mutex_);
71
72 Clock* const clock_;
73 const FieldTrialBasedConfig field_trials_;
74 SsrcOveruseEstimatorMap overuse_detectors_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(mutex_);
75 RateStatistics incoming_bitrate_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(mutex_);
76 uint32_t last_valid_incoming_bitrate_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(mutex_);
77 std::unique_ptr<AimdRateControl> remote_rate_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(mutex_);
78 RemoteBitrateObserver* const observer_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(mutex_);
79 mutable Mutex mutex_;
80 int64_t last_process_time_;
81 int64_t process_interval_ms_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(mutex_);
82 bool uma_recorded_;
83};
84
85} // namespace webrtc
86
87#endif // MODULES_REMOTE_BITRATE_ESTIMATOR_REMOTE_BITRATE_ESTIMATOR_SINGLE_STREAM_H_
